    "description": "<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350810/extras/797153a55bbe219db49d86cccc52f079.avif?t=1680660655\" width=620 height=155 /></span><br><br>Glory Room 是一款轻快上手的roguelike 游戏。<br>它继续讲述了人物的简短故事，他们别无选择，只能来到地狱般的竞技场。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350810/extras/836c91b16a51003bff761c0030b503cf.poster.avif?t=1680660655\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350810/extras/836c91b16a51003bff761c0030b503cf.webm?t=1680660655\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350810/extras/836c91b16a51003bff761c0030b503cf.mp4?t=1680660655\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>玩家的控制技巧也很重要。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350810/extras/dd571d4c41b8a1cb8a6c4f9215d9fb65.avif?t=1680660655\" width=620 height=155 /></span><br><br>有各种随机出现的特殊房间。<br>通过它，您可以强化武器、赌博或获得物品。<br>您可以通过多种方式升级您的角色。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350810/extras/0f59f2b1c871105906076d1ffd663e1b.poster.avif?t=1680660655\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350810/extras/0f59f2b1c871105906076d1ffd663e1b.webm?t=1680660655\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350810/extras/0f59f2b1c871105906076d1ffd663e1b.mp4?t=1680660655\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350810/extras/9d3cd8285ab34b80b3759f814e63b63b.avif?t=1680660655\" width=620 height=155 /></span><br><br>战斗不是唯一的方法。<br>突然袭击和有许多陷阱的房间也会出现。<br>制定自己的策略来解决问题。<br>还可以找到隐藏的物品。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350810/extras/020bd9701faf93d3277ddbba08bb14d0.poster.avif?t=1680660655\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350810/extras/020bd9701faf93d3277ddbba08bb14d0.webm?t=1680660655\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350810/extras/020bd9701faf93d3277ddbba08bb14d0.mp4?t=1680660655\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350810/extras/f6b29c4a8659ddd8040ba08603dec4e7.avif?t=1680660655\" width=620 height=155 /></span><br><br>游戏中有大量的选项技能和被动技能。<br>一些组合创造出非常强大的力量。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350810/extras/9d02a62fd6e5096ff879d92d4f930eb7.poster.avif?t=1680660655\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350810/extras/9d02a62fd6e5096ff879d92d4f930eb7.webm?t=1680660655\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350810/extras/9d02a62fd6e5096ff879d92d4f930eb7.mp4?t=1680660655\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350810/extras/05b952a6d20463aebd4d26732ecc79b0.avif?t=1680660655\" width=620 height=155 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350810/extras/28dd5463d3795b0dd1be8f6f10b80f30.avif?t=1680660655\" width=300 height=300 /></span><br><br>Glory Room 里有很多摄像头和闭路电视。<br>如果你表现出一场激情的战斗，观众会欢呼并给你钱。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350810/extras/fcdce26b370e0bf909aa94638278337e.poster.avif?t=1680660655\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350810/extras/fcdce26b370e0bf909aa94638278337e.webm?t=1680660655\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350810/extras/fcdce26b370e0bf909aa94638278337e.mp4?t=1680660655\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350810/extras/3e4836e7891116872c1fec97af916491.avif?t=1680660655\" width=620 height=155 /></span><br><br>游戏中有各种各样的武器、技能、怪物、陷阱等等。<br>如果找到这些，您可以随时查看该项目的信息和模型。<br>不幸的是，并不是所有的都是免费的。<br>在荣耀房间里赚钱以解锁所有物品。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350810/extras/cc8bee53fed7b7ac3ed1a2cc61190922.avif?t=1680660655\" width=620 height=348 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350810/extras/6cb9e895d98b727f872ada2a5315668f.avif?t=1680660655\" width=620 height=348 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350810/extras/b83714469401335f21295a9adce7c755.avif?t=1680660655\" width=620 height=155 /></span><br><br>- 添加魔法武器和长枪武器<br>- 添加电锯<br>- 增加各种被动技能物品<br>- 添加阶段<br>- 更多房型<br>- 每种武器的特殊升级技术<br>- 添加赌博对象<br>- 每个角色的故事进展<br>- 游戏平衡调整<br>- 添加和产生主动技能",
